question: List the attenuated live viruses contained in the Fluzone intradermal quadrivalent vaccine.
ideal_answer: The Fluzone Intradermal Quadrivalent vaccine contains 9 ug hemagglutinin per strain of the two A-strain viruses and both B-strain lineage viruses (Victoria and Yamagata).

snippets.text: In advance of the 2015-2016 season, Fluzone Intradermal was replaced with Fluzone Intradermal Quadrivalent vaccine, which contains 9 µg hemagglutinin per strain of the two A-strain viruses and both B-strain lineage viruses (Victoria and Yamagata).

exact_answer: strain of A/H1N1, strain of A/H3N2, B Victoria lineage, B Yamagata lineage
